high_descs: Open the microwave, take the apple out of the microwave, and close the microwave
Open the fridge, put the apple on a tray, close the fridge, wait a few seconds, and take the apple out of the fridge
Turn around, move across the room to face the red bin
Put the apple inside the bin
anns.task_desc: Take out an apple from the microwave, chilled it and put it in the bin

high_descs: Turn right, turn right at the sink and stand in front of the microwave.
Open the door to the microwave, take the apple out of the microwave, close the door.
Move to the front of the fridge to the right.
Open the fridge door, put the apple inside of the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the apple out, and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the red bin straight ahead.
Put the apple inside of the red bin.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple and put it in the red bin.

high_descs: Turn right and proceed to the front of the microwave.
Remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn right and face the front of the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and move to the front of the red trash bin.
Place the apple in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Chill the apple from the microwave in the fridge and put it in the red bin.
